<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="top"><span class="blue-text"><emphasis>Social Determinants of Health (SDOH)</emphasis></span></entry>
<entry valign="top"><span class="blue-text"><emphasis>Example of an Individual-Level Barrier</emphasis></span></entry>
<entry valign="top"><span class="blue-text"><emphasis>Example of a System-Level Barrier</emphasis></span></entry>
</row>
